  "description": {
    "canonical": "An ancient weapon designed by the Entrati for use by their Necramechs. Primary fire siphons life essence from the target to fuel a devastating secondary fire. A heavy flamethrower with surprising range. Secondary fire launches three projectiles in a fan pattern that explode, leaving a damaging area of effect for a short duration.",
    "display": "（英文：CORTEGE）英择谛为其殁世机甲所设计的古老武器。主要射击可从目标身上吸取生命精华，以助燃次要射击带来的毁灭性攻击。这把重型火焰喷射器拥有惊人的射程。次要射击可扇形投射三枚爆炸弹丸，并在短时间内留下一片破坏性区域。",
    "localizationStatus": "official-zh"
  },
